		<text>f course, HyperCard doesn’t know about the doubleBeep command, soit will never be sent automatically in response to an event. But you can send doubleBeep from the Message box or use it as a statement in other handlers.For example, the script of a card button might contain the following handler for the system message mouseUp:on mouseUp  doubleBeepend mouseUp</text>
